OL,3,CFamilies of terror attack victims
OL,4,Cexpress 'shock' at inquest conclusion
OL,6,FThe families of three men killed in a
OL,7,Fterror attack in Reading's Forbury
OL,8,FGardens have spoken of their shock and
OL,9,Fdisappointment following the
OL,10,Fconclusion of the inquest into their
OL,11,Fdeaths.
OL,13,FJames Furlong, Dr David Wails and
OL,14,FJoseph Ritchie-Bennett were stabbed to
OL,15,Fdeath as they had a picnic in the park
OL,16,Fon 20 June 2020.
OL,18,FTheir killer, Libyan refugee Khairi
OL,19,FSaadallah, is currently serving a
OL,20,Fwhole life order in prison.
