OL,6,FAt a hearing on Friday (23 February),
OL,7,FJudge Coroner Sir Adrian Fulford
OL,8,Fconfirmed he intends to give his full
OL,9,Fconclusion of the inquest on Friday 26
OL,10,FApril at the Old Bailey.
OL,12,FCounsel to the inquest and interested
OL,13,Fparties agreed that Article 2 should
OL,14,Fbe engaged.
OL,16,FThe ruling provides the court with a
OL,17,Fbigger remit and extra scope to
OL,18,Finvestigate in circumstances where an
OL,19,Findividual may have been relying on
OL,20,Fprotection from the State.
