OL,6,FThe inquest at the Old Bailey has
OL,7,Fheard substantial evidence about
OL,8,FSaadallah's extremist risk, offending
OL,9,Fhistory, and mental health issues, as
OL,10,Fwell as how his risk of harm to the
OL,11,Fpublic was assessed, managed and
OL,12,Fresponded following his release from
OL,13,Fprison on 5 June 2020 up to the terror
OL,14,Fattack itself on 20 June 2020.
