OL,3,CFamilies of terror attack victims
OL,4,Cexpress 'shock' at inquest conclusion
OL,6,FIn a statement read outside court on
OL,7,Fbehalf of the families of James
OL,8,FFurlong, Dr David Wails and Joseph
OL,9,FRitchie-Bennett, Gary Furlong, father
OL,10,Fof James Furlong said: "I speak for
OL,11,Fthe families of Joseph Ritchie-
OL,12,FBennett, Dr David Wails and my son,
OL,13,FJames Furlong.
OL,15,F"For six weeks we have listened to
OL,16,Fevidence given in the inquests into
OL,17,Fthe deaths of our beloved Joseph,
OL,18,FDavid and James.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
