OL,3,CFamilies of terror attack victims
OL,4,Cexpress 'shock' at inquest conclusion
OL,6,F"We have listened as public bodies and
OL,7,Findividuals have given their account
OL,8,Fof their dealings with Khairi
OL,9,FSaadallah in the years, months and
OL,10,Fweeks before he carried out his
OL,11,Fmurderous attack.
OL,13,F"As we have listened, our shock and
OL,14,Futter disappointment at the way these
OL,15,Fpublic bodies have functioned has
OL,16,Fdeepened. It has deepened to the point
OL,17,Fthat we fundamentally question whether
OL,18,Four faith in their combined ability to
OL,19,Fprotect our families was misplaced.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
