OL,3,CFamilies of terror attack victims
OL,4,Cexpress 'shock' at inquest conclusion
OL,6,F"Public bodies have explained the
OL,7,Fchallenge they faced in measuring and
OL,8,Fbalancing the risk that Saddallah
OL,9,Fposed. But we have heard evidence of
OL,10,Fpoor communication, meaning the
OL,11,Findividuals tasked with monitoring
OL,12,FSaadallah and protecting the public
OL,13,Fdid not have full and accurate
OL,14,Finformation about the risk of harm he
OL,15,Fposed.
OL,17,F"We trust the Judge Coroner will take
OL,18,Fall of this into account when he gives
OL,19,Fhis conclusion."
