OL,6,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,8,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,9,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,11,FThe families' solicitor Benjamin
OL,12,FBurrows said: "The families of James
OL,13,FFurlong, Dr David Wails and Joseph
OL,14,FRitchie-Bennett have listened bravely
OL,15,Fand intently to the witness evidence
OL,16,Fgiven over the past six weeks at the
OL,17,Finquest into the deaths of their loved
OL,18,Fones.
