OL,3,CFamilies of terror attack victims
OL,4,Cexpress 'shock' at inquest conclusion
OL,6,F"It has not been easy for them to
OL,7,Flisten to the detailed and candid
OL,8,Faccounts given by public bodies and
OL,9,Findividuals. and their legal team
OL,10,Fwould like to pay tribute to the
OL,11,Fdetermination they have shown.
OL,13,F"We will now wait for the Judge
OL,14,FCoroner to give his conclusion, and
OL,15,Ftrust that it will be a fair and
OL,16,Faccurate measure of any missed
OL,17,Fopportunities on the part of those
OL,18,Fpublic bodies and individuals who
OL,19,Fworked with Saadallah and had
OL,20,Fresponsibility for protecting the
OL,21,Fpublic from the risk of harm he posed."
